content: This game is amazing!!! Highly recommend getting it. It's worth it!!
Oh, you couldn't resist adding another platforming sequence with absolutely atrocious control layout, do you? At least it was not as bad as in previous games...

As always, AppSir continues his tradition to surprise me in his games, this time, was with the return of Knightly has the player's character and even with the return of AIDE and Yanna (I missed them since I played Dere Evil.Exe) I loved how the game looks, how Knightly was implemented here and even the backgrounds and music are great n.n The puzzles are challenging but that doesn't surprises me, I always know that when a game is good and made with care, it will be a challenge to the player
I almost got a refund when I first played it....then I was hooked. Simple mechanics, often hard, frustrating at times but always fun.
First game I've ever purchased. That's all you need to know about app sir games and their quality
Enjoyable game with some surprising moments, more than it initially looks
Another masterpiece by AppSir. Everything about this extremely hard retro horror comedy platformer is flawless.
The game was great, hard but still fun to play
This game was very fun but I wasn't very interested in the gameplay but it was still fun please make more games that cover the lore of this universe
Another winner by The Dev with a number of twists and turns, including a surprising final boss!

A very unique entry in the AppSir series of games. A lot more like a puzzle game with lots of challenging levels. But what is the same us everything great about AppSir: developing narrative, the horror of the unknown, ulterior motives in the characters, and more! Knightly is a great example of this. An old character reimagined in a new form. That's what Puzzling Peaks EXE is, and AppSir continues to impress with impressive creativity!
Like..wow. The game itself is amazing and hard.The fake ending caught me off guard tho LMAO
